e. Include previous work experience, education or achievements that would be beneficial. And list any preferred hard and soft skills. Example Building Maintenance Technician requirements Knowledge of mechanical systems Knowledge of company policies and procedures Experience repairing and maintaining equipment Problem solving abilities Great written and verbal communication skills A team player Building Maintenance Technician related job titles: Maintenance Tech Commercial Building Technician Commercial Building Maintenance Technician Maintenance Person Residential Maintenance Technician Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
